attributes.title: SEATTLE, WASHINGTON
attributes.caption: Geoff makes Fiona and Jack go to Seattle to see if the oldest piece of gum on the gum wall still has flavor. And to catch a few flying fish at Pike’s Place.
attributes.description: Geoff makes Fiona and Jack go to Seattle to see if the oldest piece of gum on the gum wall still has flavor. And to catch a few flying fish at Pike’s Place.

attributes.title: PARIS, FRANCE
attributes.caption: Geoff makes Trevor and Michael go all the way to Paris , France to see what it’s like to use an open air toilet, and find out if the Royale with Cheese actually exists.

attributes.title: MIDLAND, TEXAS
attributes.caption: Geoff makes Alfredo and Jack drive the rental version of his car to Midland to see how far it’ll make it on one tank of gas, oh yeah, and they have flight home that night so they should hurry.

attributes.title: PAPA WESTRAY, SCOTLAND
attributes.caption: Geoff makes Ryan and Jack see how far they can get around the world barefoot, and then see what the drink service situation is on the world's shortest commercial flight.
attributes.description: Geoff makes Ryan and Jack see how far they can get around the world barefoot, and then see what the drink service situation is on the world's shortest commercial flight.

attributes.title: MOBILE, ALABAMA
attributes.caption: Geoff makes Ryan and Matt go to his hometown to dig up a time capsule he buried as a kid, but more importantly, to go get some of his favorite food on Earth: His mom’s potato soup.

attributes.title: SEOUL, SOUTH KOREA
attributes.caption: Geoff Makes Jeremy and Alfredo go to South Korea to see if Hagfish slime tastes like eggs.
attributes.description: Geoff Makes Jeremy and Alfredo go to South Korea to see if Hagfish slime tastes like eggs.

attributes.title: MINNEAPOLIS, MINNESOTA
attributes.caption: Geoff makes Lindsay and Jeremy go to Minneapolis, Minnesota to the quietest room on earth just to see what their guts sound like. Oh yeah, and they ride a roller coaster.

attributes.title: SACRAMENTO, CALIFORNIA
attributes.caption: To get back at Geoff for sending them all over the world, the group sends him and his daughter to Sacramento to do the lowest bungee in America.
